description: Recently sold: $1,154,848. The upgrades are unbelievable in this newer built (2015) french country style home that sits on over 2 acres near Dellwood Country Club and the Pine Tree Apple Orchard.  Enjoy the in-ground salt-water heated pool, stamped concrete and composite deck added just last year!  This home comes with an Onkyo surround sound including speakers by the pool. The main floor greets you with a barrel vault ceiling as you walk into the open floor plan.  The kitchen, living room, dining area, office and porch all overlook your acres through large windows.  Built-ins are throughout this home including near the front entryway, mudroom off the garage, bedrooms and lower level.
